name: Smita’s Lakeview Restaurant & Bar |Best Fish Thali And Authentic Goan Food|

reviews.review_text: Always go and only go for starters dish as they have best cuisine and taste is good. Atmosphere is fantastic with music and lake view point. Main course like thali are okay type. Regarding service they are good for starters like bringing it  quickly but main course they take lot of time. Regarding parking space you forget. Recommended to bring Two wheeler only. It is  also expensive compare to quantity they provide. Overall is Very Good.

Everything was good, at first we thought bit pricey. But when it comes to table, actual quantity was surprisingly good. Quite place with goan music in background. Mr. Bharat served us overall food and he was friendly and a gentleman.

Hi there , I myself n my fiance visited this place when we came across to the video on instagram. I was craving to have the food from a long time while I was in abroad. Sukumar had served us very professionally. Even the food was on time n it was very mouth watering. To everyone reading this if you come to Goa n don’t visit here b eat chonok thali tho kya kaya my friend. Note :my favourite prawns papadom. Thank you

description:
## Smita’s Lakeview Restaurant & Bar: A Gem of Goan Cuisine

Nestled in the picturesque landscape of Goa, **Smita’s Lakeview Restaurant & Bar** boasts an impressive rating of **4.2** from nearly **4,000 reviews**, establishing itself as a popular dining destination for locals and tourists alike. Known for its **authentic Goan food**, especially its **Best Fish Thali**, as well as standout dishes such as **barramundi**, **mussels**, **kingfish**, and **rava fry**, this restaurant excels at delivering coastal flavors in a scenic setting.

### Ambiance & Design

As you step into Smita's, you're greeted by a vibrant atmosphere that radiates the essence of Goan culture. The décor reflects a harmonious blend of local artistry and beach vibes, vividly complemented by **soft lighting** and wooden accents that create an inviting warmth. Dining here allows guests to enjoy stunning **lake views**, which are perfectly framed by the restaurant's layout, ensuring a picturesque backdrop for an unforgettable meal. The ambiance is further enhanced by **Goan music**, drifting gently through the air, adding to the tranquil yet lively environment. Customer photos reveal serene scenes of the lake, alluring table settings, and a stunning view that makes you want to linger just a little bit longer.

### Menu & Culinary Experience

The culinary offerings at Smita’s focus heavily on seafood, making it a haven for fish enthusiasts. The **Fish Thali** is frequently praised; its robust flavors and generous portions delight diners who appreciate traditional Goan fare. Alongside, their **prawns papadom** has captured hearts, becoming a must-try for visitors. Diners rave about the **starter dishes**—especially the **rava fry**—which are served promptly, maintaining a high standard of taste and presentation. The reviews highlight that though the **main courses** might be slightly slower to arrive, they are worth the wait. The food consistently garners compliments for not just flavor but also visual appeal, making each dish a feast for the eyes as well as the palate.

### Customer Experience & Service

Reviewers generally commend the friendly and attentive service, noting servers like **Mr. Bharat** and **Sukumar** for their professionalism and ability to make guests feel welcomed. However, a few patrons have pointed out that while starters come out rapidly, the main dishes take a bit longer to prepare. Guests are encouraged to visit via **two-wheeler** due to limited parking, which can be a consideration for those arriving in larger vehicles. Despite a few mentions of higher prices relative to portions, many found the quality and experience justifiable.

### Popularity & Reviews

Customer sentiment leans positively, with a notable buzz on social media platforms where potential diners are encouraged to visit Smita’s upon their arrival in Goa. The picturesque views and flavorful dishes continue to attract attention, making it an essential stop on any foodie’s itinerary. The restaurant has solidified its reputation not only through customer reviews but also through word-of-mouth as an establishment that embodies the delicious and vibrant culinary traditions of the region.

### Utilizing Visual Content

The visuals shared by customers capture the essence of dining at Smita’s Lakeview Restaurant beautifully. Images portray the elegant presentation of the Fish Thali, showcasing a riot of colors that promise a delightful taste experience (see one such image [here](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdkVT9qDdx7P-2wiWJ8n4ga8JlExVp5jPhb6RYrx9b2y_V4wYutSV64DXUvsah-FfZP8JE6TZxL15aoIcxugUPVOrmbmm2SuE3D65l72H9kmuUFxoYsQea3MZI7zdLk5iV9kZrk54g=w375-h281-p) for inspiration). Stunning lake views and cozy setup contribute to its inviting aesthetic, ensuring guests enjoy every moment—captured perfectly in customer snapshots.

In conclusion, for those seeking **authentic Goan cuisine** with exceptional views, **Smita’s Lakeview Restaurant & Bar** delivers on taste, atmosphere, and attentive service, making it a must-visit for anyone exploring the vibrant culinary scene of Goa. Indulging in the flavors here guarantees not just a meal, but a delightful experience that resonates long after the last bite.
